reviewText: The video was OK to watch and get started I guess, but if you have played around at all with your harmonica you probably are beyond this video.  Not a lot in it to "work on".

I find that Jimmy was very thro whengoing through each step. The positions of the lips and toung when blowing , drawing and bending notes was done exceptionaly well. Anyone who wishes to learn to play harmonica will  definately benefit from this tape.
